    <item>
      <title>由于收入前景下调，Truist 的贷款收入未达预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/truist-s-lending-income-misses-estimates-as-revenue-forecast-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Truist Financial Corp.公布的第一季度贷款利润低于分析师预期，因为该公司被迫在利率保持高位的情况下向客户支付更多存款，并且该银行还下调了今年剩余时间的收入指引。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/truist-s-lending-income-misses-estimates-as-revenue-forecast-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 10:20:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罢工后中东紧张局势缓和，金价回落</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/gold-backtracks-as-middle-east-tensions-ease-following-strikes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着中东地缘政治紧张局势缓和、避险需求减少，以及交易员期待美国数据将揭示货币政策前景，金价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/gold-backtracks-as-middle-east-tensions-ease-following-strikes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 02:03:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国期货上涨，大型科技公司盈利成为焦点：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/asian-traders-brace-for-key-data-us-futures-rise-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着投资者的注意力从中东紧张局势转向本周计划发布的大量公司财报，美国股指期货上涨，其中包括主导去年牛市的“七大”科技巨头中的四家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/asian-traders-brace-for-key-data-us-futures-rise-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 22:28:51 GMT</pubDate>
